query:
SELECT t.id, t.codigo, e.id as eventoId, e.nomeEvento, e.dataEvento 
FROM turmas t 
JOIN eventos e ON e.turmaId = t.id 
WHERE e.dataEvento IS NOT NULL 
LIMIT 5
